body:
(1) Please review tensorflow guidelines [here](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/ISSUE_TEMPLATE.md) before raising an issue.
(2) Please go to [stackoverflow](https://stackoverflow.com/search?q=install+tensorflow+on+windows) for more help.
(3) If you are trying to install tensorflow-gpu then have to follow specific guidelines [here](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/42011070/on-windows-running-import-tensorflow-generates-no-module-named-pywrap-tenso).
(4) If you are trying to install tensorflow without gpu support then read and follow installation guidelines [here](https://www.tensorflow.org/install/install_windows).
